---
import Layout from "../layouts/Page.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Work Experience"
  description="Professional experience of Isiah Fletcher: 4+ years in React development at Hinge Health, expertise in TypeScript, design systems, and full-stack engineering. View detailed resume and technical skills."
>
  <!-- Hero Intro -->
  <section class="resume-intro">
    <p>
      I build digital solutions and drum-driven storms. From shaping Hinge
      Health’s React design system to igniting stages with thunderous beats, I’m
      the kind of engineer-and-artist you can’t ignore.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Highlights -->
  <section class="resume-highlights">
    <h2>Quick Hits</h2>
    <div class="highlights-grid">
      <div class="highlight-item">
        <strong>4+ Years</strong>
        crafting React interfaces & design systems in digital health tech
      </div>
      <div class="highlight-item">
        <strong>Session Drummer</strong>
        across rock, jazz, funk, pop & metal—bringing grooves to life
      </div>
      <div class="highlight-item">
        <strong>Polyglot Coder</strong>
        JavaScript · TypeScript · Rust · React · Node.js · Actix-web
      </div>
      <div class="highlight-item">
        <strong>Storyteller</strong>
        poet & gamer—writing micro-stories and shaping worlds when not coding
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Professional Experience -->
  <section class="resume-section">
    <h2>Professional Experience</h2>

    <div class="job">
      <h3>Hinge Health — Full Stack Developer</h3>
      <p class="job-meta">Mar 2023 &ndash; Present | Boise, ID</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Led the end-to-end deprecation of legacy modules, trimming technical
          debt by 60% and boosting performance.
        </li>
        <li>
          Designed & implemented a brand-new design token system, saving $100K+
          in rebranding and refactor costs.
        </li>
        <li>
          Served as the bridge between design, PM, and front-end teams—ensuring
          pixel-perfect React components ship on schedule.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="job">
      <h3>Foundry Interactive — Front-End Developer</h3>
      <p class="job-meta">Jan 2021 &ndash; Feb 2023 | Boise, ID</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Built a library of accessible React components, cutting new feature
          time by 40%.
        </li>
        <li>
          Authored robust API endpoints in Ruby on Rails; integrated Cypress and
          Jest for 90% test coverage.
        </li>
        <li>
          Drove Agile sprints in a high-velocity CI/CD pipeline—shipping weekly
          releases without rollback.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="job">
      <h3>Ventive — Project Manager Intern</h3>
      <p class="job-meta">Jun 2020 &ndash; Oct 2020 | Boise, ID</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Coordinated between clients and dev teams—scoping work, writing JIRA
          tickets, hosting daily scrums.
        </li>
        <li>
          Conducted QA sweeps and code reviews that caught 95% of critical bugs
          before release.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Technical Skills -->
  <section class="resume-section">
    <h2>Technical Arsenal</h2>
    <ul class="skills-grid">
      <li><strong>Languages:</strong> JavaScript, TypeScript, Rust</li>
      <li><strong>Frameworks:</strong> React, Node.js, Actix-web, Next.js</li>
      <li>
        <strong>Tools:</strong> Storybook, Git, Cypress, Jest, GraphQL, NestJS
      </li>
      <li><strong>Databases:</strong> MySQL, MongoDB, Mongoose</li>
      <li><strong>Other:</strong> Contentful, Docker, OAuth2</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- Education -->
  <section class="resume-section">
    <h2>Education & Certifications</h2>

    <h3>Full Stack Software Dev Certificate — Coding Dojo</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Built 10+ full-stack apps with JavaScript frameworks and vanilla JS.
      </li>
      <li>
        Integrated Auth0/OAuth2; practiced Git workflows in team projects.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3>B.A. in Creative Writing — University of Idaho (2013–2016)</h3>
    <p>Forged a passion for storytelling and poetic brevity.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .resume-intro p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* New Quick Hits Styling */
  .resume-highlights {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .resume-highlights h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .highlights-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .highlight-item {
    background: var(--accent-lightest);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-dark);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .highlight-item strong {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--accent-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .resume-section h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }
  .job {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .job-meta {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .skills-grid li {
    background: var(--accent-lightest);
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
</style>
